Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.38,0:37:28.89,sign_53836_662_Affinity_Fire__0,,0000,0000,0000,,Affinity\NFire: 0\NWater: 0\NIce: 0\NWind: 0\NEarth: 0\NLightning: 0\NLight: 0\NDark: 0
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.38,0:37:28.89,sign_53836_663_Equipment_Small_,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment\NSmall Shield\NHemp Outfit\NRagged Cape
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.68,0:37:28.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I fight all night and finally hit Level 2, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.81,0:37:47.12,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:37:50.09,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,How does 1 copper for a pair sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:51.87,main,Adv,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.31,0:37:53.62,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.54,0:37:57.07,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.84,0:38:00.96,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.78,0:38:06.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.95,0:38:09.93,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Orange balloons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.41,0:38:12.66,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.66,0:38:15.44,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,How does 1 copper sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.83,0:38:20.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you offer that guy 1 copper for two?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.70,0:38:23.24,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Did I, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.24,0:38:25.96,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,You must understand,\NI have a business to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.96,0:38:26.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.63,0:38:30.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will these things fetch \Na better price, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.95,0:38:32.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.32,0:38:35.00,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.33,0:38:37.09,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.09,0:38:39.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to rip you off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.09,0:38:41.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is a fair market price.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.76,0:38:45.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, do you hate me \Nfor some reason, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:47.73,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.73,0:38:49.64,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, so get these things off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.74,0:38:52.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.27,0:38:55.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of trying to fleece me, \Nif you buy from me regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.95,0:38:57.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to give you a small discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.98,0:39:00.34,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,C-Consider it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.34,0:39:06.64,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,As much as I'd like to refuse,\N the goods and money are without sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:11.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Also, feel free to tell people all about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.28,0:39:15.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them that any trader that messes with \Nme will end up with bite marks all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:17.94,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,No need to ask me. I was \Nabout to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.94,0:39:20.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,To a long business relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.80,0:39:50.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:55.98,sign_33122_363_Legendary_Weapon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}New Shields Unlocked
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.87,0:40:01.38,sign_57539_699_There_are_shield,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,190)}There are shields with available skill unlocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.13,0:40:04.09,sign_57618_700_Mastery_Bonus_Wh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)}Mastery Bonus\N\N{\fs12}When a shield is used for a while to achieve a certain level of proficiency,\N it will grant its wielder permanent bonuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:10.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So by mastering a shield, I can keep its\Nabilities even after I switch to another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.38,0:40:13.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Leaf Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.83,0:40:22.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This really is like a game, \Nthrough and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.06,0:40:28.48,sign_58168_704_Foraging_Skill_1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1448,1)}Foraging Skill 1 Activated\NAero: *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.79,0:40:30.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It can improve the mat's quality?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.84,0:40:38.28,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.28,0:40:39.76,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.76,0:40:41.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In the forest right outside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.97,0:40:43.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.31,0:40:47.41,main,Herb,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I never knew you could \Nfind such fine stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.41,0:40:49.69,main,Herb,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure the quality was more average.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.03,0:41:01.54,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day,\Nnothing I eat has any flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.54,0:41:03.66,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,O Great Shield Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.66,0:41:05.83,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,we'll join your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.83,0:41:08.94,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Thank your lucky stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:14.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ahead and discuss the terms first.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.63,0:41:16.76,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.76,0:41:19.76,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Your pay will be entirely performance-based.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.76,0:41:21.14,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.14,0:41:23.02,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, no clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.27,0:41:27.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It means you'll be paid according to \Nthe loot we get on our adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.48,0:41:32.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader, so I'll \Ntake at least 40 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.90,0:41:35.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll split the rest at my discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.45,0:41:40.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you do nothing, you get paid nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.03,0:41:45.25,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? That means you could \Nkeep it all for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.25,0:41:47.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to pay you if you do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.62,0:41:49.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If{\i0} you can do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.71,0:41:53.25,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get us some equipment, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.80,0:41:55.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Buy your equipment yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.97,0:41:59.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to do that much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.30,0:41:59.99,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.99,0:42:03.35,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Just hand over your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.78,0:42:07.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd said that to begin with, \Nwe could've saved some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.27,0:42:09.10,main,PunkC,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.10,0:42:10.69,main,PunkC,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you awfully obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:16.22,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,Quit freakin' out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.07,0:42:20.53,main,PunkA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.99,0:42:24.03,main,PunkB,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.83,0:42:33.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have the defense,\N but lack offensive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.00,0:42:35.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Because I lack it, I can't defeat monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.55,0:42:38.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And because I can't defeat \Nthem, I can't farm EXP.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.56,0:42:42.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And because I can't farm,\Nmy offensive ability never goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.05,0:42:44.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What an awful loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.79,0:42:45.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.35,0:42:54.73,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.11,0:43:02.22,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.22,0:43:04.98,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,But I have just what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.27,0:43:07.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you're offering me party members,\N thanks but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.68,0:43:08.77,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Party members?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.77,0:43:14.25,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Please. What I'm offering you is \Na service far more convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.99,0:43:16.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.85,0:43:18.50,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Interested, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.50,0:43:19.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.48,0:43:24.77,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,That look in your eyes \Nis the kind I just love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.77,0:43:27.39,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You're every bit the man \Nthe rumors said you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:29.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.67,0:43:33.12,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.47,0:43:37.79,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,If my offer interests you, please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.15,0:43:51.70,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.73,0:43:57.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly are you offering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.53,0:44:00.36,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell at a glance?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.75,0:44:02.76,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.76,0:44:03.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Slaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.32,0:44:07.71,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I run a slave trading business.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.69,0:44:11.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think I want a slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.66,0:44:17.38,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that they cannot \Nlie or betray their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.94,0:44:21.62,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Slaves are placed under \Nthe effect of a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.01,0:44:27.10,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,A strong, seal-based curse that \Ncan take their very lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.77,0:44:29.29,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.03,0:44:32.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.68,0:44:37.60,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. You have everything it \Ntakes to be a most wonderful patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.63,0:44:42.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see ones that aren't human, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.68,0:44:45.20,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You can call them human, technically.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.69,0:44:49.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more. I don't know \Nmuch about this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.85,0:44:55.81,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Creatures that look human but \Naren't are called demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.81,0:44:59.61,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,They're mostly used in manual \Nlabor or as servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.61,0:45:04.31,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Beastmen are demi-humans whose appearance \Nleans more toward the animal side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.31,0:45:09.31,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,They're used as bodyguards or as participants\N in death matches that are gambled on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.31,0:45:10.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.39,0:45:12.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But they both fall under \Nthe same category, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.72,0:45:17.64,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. And since demi-humans are \Nthought to be closer to monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.64,0:45:21.30,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,life would be hard for them in this country,\N which practices human supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.30,0:45:24.62,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,As such, they're treated as slaves.
